<strong>Luckily for you, with promo code "hoppytimes" you can get your hands on tickets for just $20 <a href="http://www.eventbrite.com/e/river-north-beer-fest-tickets-16564292244?aff=HoppyTimes" target="_blank">here</a>. That's $30 off what the other folks are paying!</strong>

